{"tid":886131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"102歲人瑞性侵92歲阿嬤 最高恐判7年刑","createTime":"2018-11-02T01:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T04:51:26.000Z","uid":35468,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d665cb8ecd2c34c484aecacba481e0bfbb0c1103","tid":886131,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:16:01.000Z","msg":"澳洲警方今（24）日表示，一名102歲的人瑞爺爺涉嫌性侵一名92歲阿嬤而被警方逮捕，最高將面臨7年的有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n據《法新社》報導，事件發生於澳洲雪梨邦代海灘（Bondi Beach）附近的老人安養院，警方於23日中午接獲報案，隨即前往現場逮捕這名高齡人瑞，而對於詳細案情與嫌疑犯姓名，警方則尚未公布。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，該名嫌犯已經被保釋，並將於11月20日出庭，最高可能被判7年徒刑。報導指出，少數老人因過去所犯下的罪而被判刑，但超過百歲的人瑞犯案則相當罕見。"},{"pid":"48bc33d5759a05e78ccf861e7acfac900a00d83c","tid":886131,"uid":19712,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:16:40.000Z","msg":"就算過100歲都有性需要"},{"pid":"ba931d5dd8d3c9f28d0375a8fadcedb716b2bdd3","tid":886131,"uid":33939,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"點解冇人關注下長者性福？"},{"pid":"5714630ab318fdacac1de39e6fefbac8007ac615","tid":886131,"uid":90820,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"而家啲90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb1ad76cf1b1ea2bfe6461f5fc2864d42fb7226","tid":886131,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5714630ab318fdacac1de39e6fefbac8007ac615","tid":886131,"uid":90820,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"而家啲90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8431e272dd6be8a8ec84dc224ba2ea1244f986","tid":886131,"uid":62532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01